                "name": "Refuse Pile",
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "ability",
                "ability_type": "interaction",
                "text": "When it\u2019s not in danger, an ofalth can spend 1 minute settling into a 10-foot pile that looks like a heap of garbage. While doing so, the ofalth gains a +2 circumstance bonus to AC but can\u2019t use attack, manipulate, or move actions. A creature that enters the area of the garbage heap or interacts with it must attempt a save against the ofalth\u2019s putrid stench and wretched weeps disease. An ofalth can leave this form using a single action."
            }
